{"tid":2326233,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"疫情持續延燒 日本破例允許無工作資格的外國人打零工","createTime":"2020-12-15T07:39:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-16T12:20:46.000Z","uid":75969,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"5a860456f064a93134fd18a1a98337c7420b4c54","tid":2326233,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T07:39:35.000Z","msg":"〔財經頻道／綜合報導〕武漢肺炎（新型冠狀病毒病，COVID-19）大流行，導致許多外國人無法回國需滯留在日本。鑒於因疫情難以回國的外國人數漸增，為加快改善外國人勞動的環境，日本政府破例允許無工作資格外國人打零工。<br />\n<br />\n《日經中文網》報導，繼早前允許外國實習生「轉行」工作後，日本政府現又再次放寬外國人打工規範，破例允許因疫情影響被滯留日本、生活無以為繼的外國人，可以打零工方式參與工作，但每週工作時間不得超過28小時，上述政策自12月開始實施。<br />\n<br />\n--------------------<br />\n------------<br />\n-----<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3381886\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3381886&d=ZAqn3h4t0e4XfOyVRCtvGNmOP5%2FvN4RyP%2Fy1e26q30o%3D&h=eb1a326e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3381886&h=0bf7dcd6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3381886</a>"},{"pid":"389b58d84d6ce032189c7064a359628859fec3c8","tid":2326233,"uid":78243,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T07:40:17.000Z","msg":"姐係玩死自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee084c04e32e9f12a9d4664013d40a5c622dd8d2","tid":2326233,"uid":58948,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T07:46:40.000Z","msg":"番得果廿幾個鐘，請個外國人溝通同文化未必適應<br />\n日本仔會請咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f626871d170a50cd843680b4736f7e8a65a4512d","tid":2326233,"uid":39668,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5a860456f064a93134fd18a1a98337c7420b4c54","tid":2326233,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T07:39:35.000Z","msg":"〔財經頻道／綜合報導〕武漢肺炎（新型冠狀病毒病，COVID-19）大流行，導致許多外國人無法回國需滯留在日本。鑒於因疫情難以回國的外國人數漸增，為